associated pin states. Keep every hardware block disabled for boards to
opt in.
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/hamoa.dtsi | 336 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 336 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/hamoa.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/hamoa.dtsi
index 051dee076..1d6d909ed 100644
