From 00cece0b87c40c76c14b6c7ab68a6d3603554614 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: turbinebmw <turbine.bmw@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 17:32:14 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 04/13] media: i2c: add Surface Pro 11 camera sensors

Add an IMX681 driver, extend OV13858 with the Surface Pro 11 rear-camera
mode, and import the VD55G0 driver and sensor patches from
STMicroelectronics.

The IMX681 and OV13858 mode sequences are independently authored
representations of runtime I2C transactions observed on the hardware. No
vendor binary or extracted configuration payload is included.

The VD55G0 files are adapted under GPL-2.0 from STMicroelectronics
vd55g0-linux-driver revision:

  9134fe572b77f906344f37ba227f375db73dc026
