From b1eae4e601697ffe783b47c052f1bc5d37cb9917 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: turbinebmw <turbine.bmw@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 17:32:14 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 06/13] media: qcom: camss: support X1E80100 C-PHY links

Accept C-PHY endpoints, propagate the PHY mode into CSID, select the
X1E80100 receive clocks, and configure the 4 nm 3PH v2.1.2 PHY for the
IMX681 link.

The common, lane, interrupt, and 2.5-Gsym/s data-rate tables are adapted
under GPL-2.0-only from Qualcomm cam_csiphy_2_1_2_hwreg.h blob:

  347fb4944ccedfead1aa0c5260e6b41a5a038017

The Surface-specific lane-enable value is an independent runtime
observation.
