Subject: [PATCH 10/13] arm64: dts: qcom: denali: preserve ath12k rfkill quirk

The WCN7850 firmware reaches mission mode but does not register a
wireless PHY when ath12k configures its firmware rfkill input on
Denali. Bluetooth is unaffected because it uses a separate UART
transport.

Restore the board property consumed by the Dale Whinham devicetree
rfkill support and record the dependency in the provenance document.
---
 .../driver-api/media/sp11-camera-provenance.rst          | 9 +++++++++
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/x1-microsoft-denali.dtsi        | 3 +++
 2 files changed, 12 insertions(+)

